<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Affidavit</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 1in;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 6.5in;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #0056b3;
            margin-bottom: 0.5in;
            font-size: 24pt;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 0.2in;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .content {
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .form-field {
            margin: 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            min-width: 150px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .field-value {
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #000;
            min-height: 20px;
            padding: 2px 5px;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 0.75in;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            width: 3in;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-top: 0.2in;
            padding-top: 0.05in;
        }
        .date-place {
            margin-top: 0.5in;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 1in;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .italic {
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .underline {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .indent {
            text-indent: 0.5in;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>AFFIDAVIT</h1>

        <div class="section">
            I, <span class="bold underline">{{ deponent_name | default("[Deponent's Full Name]") }}</span>, son/daughter/wife of <span class="bold underline">{{ deponent_father_name | default("[Deponent's Father/Husband's Name]") }}</span>, aged about <span class="bold underline">{{ deponent_age | default("[Age]") }}</span> years, by occupation <span class="bold underline">{{ deponent_occupation | default("[Occupation]") }}</span>, residing at <span class="bold underline">{{ deponent_address | default("[Deponent's Full Address]") }}</span>, do hereby solemnly affirm and declare as under:
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Deponent Details:</div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Name:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ deponent_name | default('[Your Full Name]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Father's Name/Husband's Name:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ deponent_father_name | default("[Deponent's Father/Husband's Name]") }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Age:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ deponent_age | default("[Age]") }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Occupation:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ deponent_occupation | default("[Occupation]") }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Address:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ deponent_address | default("[Deponent's Full Address]") }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Statement of Facts:</div>
            <div class="content">
                <ol>
                    <li>That I am the deponent herein and am well conversant with the facts and circumstances hereunder stated.</li>
                    <li>That the facts stated herein below are true and correct to the best of my knowledge and belief.</li>
                    <li>That the contents of this affidavit are based on my personal knowledge and records.</li>
                    <li>That I state that <span class="bold underline">{{ statement_of_facts | default("[Statement of Facts/Details of the Case]") }}</span>.</li>
                    <li>That this affidavit is being filed for the purpose of <span class="bold underline">{{ purpose | default("[Purpose of Affidavit]") }}</span>.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p class="bold">VERIFICATION:</p>
            <p class="indent">I, the above named deponent, do hereby verify on this <span class="bold underline">{{ date_of_affidavit | default("[Date of Affidavit]") }}</span> at <span class="bold underline">{{ place_of_affidavit | default("[Place of Affidavit]") }}</span> that the contents of the above affidavit are true and correct to my knowledge and belief and nothing material has been concealed therefrom.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <p>Deponent</p>
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <p class="bold">{{ deponent_name | default("[Deponent's Full Name]") }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="date-place">
            <p>Date: {{ current_date }}</p>
            <p>Place: {{ place_of_affidavit | default("[Place of Affidavit]") }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Note: This is a draft affidavit. It should be reviewed and attested by a Notary Public or Oath Commissioner.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
